        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nRich, usually the way to handle a merge conflict is to rebase, resolve conflicts and resubmit change under same change review. This facilitates review and keeps context of review and history intact.\n\n'git checkout master' ---> 'git fetch origin master' ----> 'git rebase -i origin/master <branch>' ---> 'git push ssh://<user-name>@gerrit.onap.org:29418/ccsdk/sli/adaptors HEAD:                    refs/for/master'",
